Package: doltr
Title: A client for the dolt database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Noam",
           family = "Ross",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noam.ross@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2136-0000")),
      person("EcoHealth Alliance", role = c("cph"))
          )
Description: Creates a DBI-compliant interface to dolt databases
    (<https://www.dolthub.com>). Also manages local dolt server processes, 
    provides convenience functions for dolt versioning, and an RStudio
    connection pane interface.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://ecohealthalliance.github.io/doltr, https://github.com/ecohealthalliance/doltr
BugReports: https://github.com/ecohealthalliance/doltr/issues
